vorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#primaryimage\"}, \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Ultimate-Creamy-Baked-Mac-and-Cheese-feat.jpg\", \"datePublished\": \"2019-10-01T00:49:54+00:00\", \"dateModified\": \"2021-11-20T02:36:21+00:00\", \"description\": \"Deliciously rich and gooey, this baked mac and cheese is creamy, comforting, and PERFECT for the holidays, as well as a comforting family dinner!\", \"breadcrumb\": {\"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#breadcrumb\"}, \"inLanguage\": \"en-US\", \"potentialAction\": [{\"@type\": \"ReadAction\", \"target\": [\"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/\"]}]}, {\"@type\": \"ImageObject\", \"inLanguage\": \"en-US\", \"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#primaryimage\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Ultimate-Creamy-Baked-Mac-and-Cheese-feat.jpg\", \"contentUrl\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Ultimate-Creamy-Baked-Mac-and-Cheese-feat.jpg\", \"width\": 440, \"height\": 550, \"caption\": \"Rich and creamy homemade baked mac and cheese, filled with multiple layers of shredded cheeses, smothered in a smooth cheese sauce, and baked until bubbly and perfect!\"}, {\"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\", \"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#breadcrumb\", \"itemListElement\": [{\"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"name\": \"Home\", \"item\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/\"}, {\"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"name\": \"Holidays and Events\", \"item\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/holidays-and-events/\"}, {\"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"name\": \"Thanksgiving Recipes\", \"item\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/holidays-and-events/thanksgiving/\"}, {\"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"name\": \"Classic sides\", \"item\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/holidays-and-events/thanksgiving/classic-sides/\"}, {\"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 5, \"name\": \"Creamy Baked Mac and Cheese\"}]}, {\"@type\": \"WebSite\", \"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/#website\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/\", \"name\": \"The Chunky Chef\", \"description\": \"Comforting Family Recipes\", \"publisher\": {\"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/#organization\"}, \"potentialAction\": [{\"@type\": \"SearchAction\", \"target\": {\"@type\": \"EntryPoint\", \"urlTemplate\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/?s={search_term_string}\"}, \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"}], \"inLanguage\": \"en-US\"}, {\"@type\": \"Organization\", \"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/#organization\", \"name\": \"The Chunky Chef LLC\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/\", \"logo\": {\"@type\": \"ImageObject\", \"inLanguage\": \"en-US\", \"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/#/schema/logo/image/\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/publisher-logo-680x680-1.jpg\", \"contentUrl\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/publisher-logo-680x680-1.jpg\", \"width\": 680, \"height\": 680, \"caption\": \"The Chunky Chef LLC\"}, \"image\": {\"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/#/schema/logo/image/\"}, \"sameAs\": [\"http://facebook.com/thechunkychef\", \"https://twitter.com/The_Chunky_Chef\", \"http://pinterest.com/thechunkychef\"]}, {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/#/schema/person/f035b2e4119e88a9b7167960b705023f\", \"name\": \"The Chunky Chef\", \"description\": \"Hey there! I'm Amanda. Wife, mother, photography nerd, and bacon lover! I believe that delicious meals should be easy to make. Now that you\\u2019re here, stay a bit, browse a few recipes, and let\\u2019s get cookin\\u2019!\", \"sameAs\": [\"http://thechunkychef.com/about/\", \"www.facebook.com/thechunkychef\", \"https://twitter.com/The_Chunky_Chef\"]}, {\"@type\": \"Recipe\", \"name\": \"Creamy Homemade Baked Mac and Cheese\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"The Chunky Chef\"}, \"description\": \"This baked mac and cheese is a family favorite recipe, loved by children and adults.\", \"datePublished\": \"2019-09-30T20:49:54+00:00\", \"image\": [\"https://www.thechunkychef.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Ultimate-Creamy-Baked-Mac-and-Cheese-feat-1.jpg\", \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Ultimate-Creamy-Baked-Mac-and-Cheese-feat-1-440x500.jpg\", \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Ultimate-Creamy-Baked-Mac-and-Cheese-feat-1-440x375.jpg\", \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Ultimate-Creamy-Baked-Mac-and-Cheese-feat-1-440x270.jpg\"], \"video\": {\"name\": \"Mac n Cheese Rec\", \"description\": \"This baked mac and cheese is a family favorite recipe, loved by both children and adults.  My version uses a combination of cheeses for a gloriously cheesy dish!\", \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://mediavine-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/s--qLhBiqEp--/c_limit,f_auto,fl_lossy,h_1080,q_auto,w_1920/v1616078221/nijjpdbtgxd0m7cszaiz.jpg\", \"embedUrl\": \"https://video.mediavine.com/videos/iVcxSy8F4.js\", \"contentUrl\": \"https://mediavine-res.cloudinary.com/video/upload/t_original/v1616078219/iVcxSy8F4.mp4\", \"uploadDate\": \"2018-03-27T00:33:21+00:00\", \"duration\": \"PT105S\", \"@type\": \"VideoObject\"}, \"recipeYield\": [\"8\", \"8 - 10 servings\"], \"prepTime\": \"PT20M\", \"cookTime\": \"PT15M\", \"totalTime\": \"PT35M\", \"recipeIngredient\": [\"1 lb. dried elbow pasta\", \"1/2 cup unsalted butter\", \"1/2 cup all purpose flour\", \"1 1/2 cups whole milk\", \"2 1/2 cups half and half\", \"4 cups shredded medium cheddar cheese (divided (measured after shredding))\", \"2 cups shredded Gruyere cheese (divided (measured after shredding))\", \"1/2 Tbsp. salt\", \"1/2 tsp. black pepper\", \"1/4 tsp. paprika (smoked paprika is our favorite!)\"], \"recipeInstructions\": [{\"@type\": \"HowToStep\", \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 325 degrees F and grease a 3 qt baking dish (9x13\\\"). &nbsp;Set aside.\", \"name\": \"Preheat oven to 325 degrees F and grease a 3 qt baking dish (9x13\\\"). &nbsp;Set aside.\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#wprm-recipe-9151-step-0-0\"}, {\"@type\": \"HowToStep\", \"text\": \"Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil. &nbsp;When boiling, add dried pasta and cook 1 minute less than the package directs for al dente. &nbsp;Drain and drizzle with a little bit of olive oil to keep from sticking.\", \"name\": \"Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil. &nbsp;When boiling, add dried pasta and cook 1 minute less than the package directs for al dente. &nbsp;Drain and drizzle with a little bit of olive oil to keep from sticking.\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#wprm-recipe-9151-step-0-1\"}, {\"@type\": \"HowToStep\", \"text\": \"While water is coming up to a boil, shred cheeses and toss together to mix, then divide into three piles. \\u00a0Approximately 3 cups for the sauce, 1 1/2 cups for the inner layer, and 1 1/2 cups for the topping.\", \"name\": \"While water is coming up to a boil, shred cheeses and toss together to mix, then divide into three piles. \\u00a0Approximately 3 cups for the sauce, 1 1/2 cups for the inner layer, and 1 1/2 cups for the topping.\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#wprm-recipe-9151-step-0-2\"}, {\"@type\": \"HowToStep\", \"text\": \"Melt butter in a large saucepan over MED heat. \\u00a0Sprinkle in flour and whisk to combine. \\u00a0Mixture will look like very wet sand. \\u00a0Cook for approximately 1 minute, whisking often. \\u00a0Slowly pour in about 2 cups or so of the half and half, while whisking constantly, until smooth. \\u00a0Slowly pour in the remaining half and half and the whole milk, while whisking constantly, until combined and smooth.\", \"name\": \"Melt butter in a large saucepan over MED heat. \\u00a0Sprinkle in flour and whisk to combine. \\u00a0Mixture will look like very wet sand. \\u00a0Cook for approximately 1 minute, whisking often. \\u00a0Slowly pour in about 2 cups or so of the half and half, while whisking constantly, until smooth. \\u00a0Slowly pour in the remaining half and half and the whole milk, while whisking constantly, until combined and smooth.\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#wprm-recipe-9151-step-0-3\"}, {\"@type\": \"HowToStep\", \"text\": \"Continue to heat over MED heat, whisking very often, until thickened to a very thick consistency. &nbsp;It should almost be the consistency of a semi thinned out condensed soup.\", \"name\": \"Continue to heat over MED heat, whisking very often, until thickened to a very thick consistency. &nbsp;It should almost be the consistency of a semi thinned out condensed soup.\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#wprm-recipe-9151-step-0-4\"}, {\"@type\": \"HowToStep\", \"text\": \"Remove from the heat and stir in spices and 1 1/2 cups of the cheeses, stirring to melt and combine. \\u00a0Stir in another 1 1/2 cups of cheese, and stir until completely melted and smooth.\", \"name\": \"Remove from the heat and stir in spices and 1 1/2 cups of the cheeses, stirring to melt and combine. \\u00a0Stir in another 1 1/2 cups of cheese, and stir until completely melted and smooth.\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#wprm-recipe-9151-step-0-5\"}, {\"@type\": \"HowToStep\", \"text\": \"In a large mixing bowl, combine drained pasta with cheese sauce, stirring to combine fully. \\u00a0Pour half of the pasta mixture into the prepared baking dish. \\u00a0Top with 1 1/2 cups of shredded cheeses, then top that with the remaining pasta mixture.\", \"name\": \"In a large mixing bowl, combine drained pasta with cheese sauce, stirring to combine fully. \\u00a0Pour half of the pasta mixture into the prepared baking dish. \\u00a0Top with 1 1/2 cups of shredded cheeses, then top that with the remaining pasta mixture.\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#wprm-recipe-9151-step-0-6\"}, {\"@type\": \"HowToStep\", \"text\": \"Sprinkle the top with the last 1 1/2 cups of cheese and bake for 15 minutes, until cheesy is bubbly and lightly golden brown. \\u00a0\", \"name\": \"Sprinkle the top with the last 1 1/2 cups of cheese and bake for 15 minutes, until cheesy is bubbly and lightly golden brown. \\u00a0\", \"url\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#wprm-recipe-9151-step-0-7\"}], \"aggregateRating\": {\"@type\": \"AggregateRating\", \"ratingValue\": \"4.85\", \"ratingCount\": \"2792\"}, \"recipeCategory\": [\"Main Course\", \"Side Dish\"], \"recipeCuisine\": [\"American\"], \"keywords\": \"mac and cheese, macaroni and cheese\", \"nutrition\": {\"@type\": \"NutritionInformation\", \"calories\": \"665 kcal\", \"carbohydrateContent\": \"43 g\", \"proteinContent\": \"28 g\", \"fatContent\": \"41 g\", \"saturatedFatContent\": \"25 g\", \"cholesterolContent\": \"126 mg\", \"sodiumContent\": \"700 mg\", \"fiberContent\": \"1 g\", \"sugarContent\": \"3 g\", \"servingSize\": \"1 serving\"}, \"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#recipe\", \"isPartOf\": {\"@id\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/#article\"}, \"mainEntityOfPage\": \"https://www.thechunkychef.com/family-favorite-baked-mac-and-cheese/\"}]}"}
